Package de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.ast

All classes needed to represent a EBNF syntax as a semantic model in an Abstract Syntax Tree.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Composite Represents an object in the AST model which can have some child nodes.
Node Interface of an AST node.
Visitable  
Visitor Defines interface for an AST tree visitor.
 

Class Summary
AbstractComposite Abstract base class for nodes which are not leaves and have sub nodes.
AbstractNode Abstract representation of AST nodes which are not the "root node" but any other kind of Node.
DepthCalculator Encapsulates the algorithm to calculate the depth of an Composite node.
Notification Used to notify collected AST errors.
 

Enum Summary
NodeType Represents the type of an EBNF node type.
 

Package de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.ast Description

All classes needed to represent a EBNF syntax as a semantic model in an Abstract Syntax Tree.

This package is a part of the open-source EBNF library
